              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="mt-2 pl-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <ul class="list-disc ml-4 space-y-1">
            <li><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1SX2VdGqUhaLO5HOMDiE97v_u6KIxgmx5/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank" class="no-underline hover:text-purple-700">FPBS UPI Annual Performance Report – 2022</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1k0AAW56L5VoUSXOw0f4BnIaMm3o8TCfb/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank" class="no-underline hover:text-purple-700">FPBS UPI Mid-Year Performance Report – 2023</a></li>
