          <span class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="mt-2 pl-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <ul class="list-disc ml-4 space-y-1">
            <li><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1aG35fBjfAG_1GE5Gog0cEYYAh4aWoC5k/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank" class="no-underline hover:text-purple-700">Dean – Prof. Dr. Tri Indri Hardini, M.Pd.</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1VQ0Wg5BvglJh5W_OeQuBjAz1Gz3HOopJ/view?usp=sharing" target="_blank" class="no-underline hover:text-purple-700">Vice Dean for Academics – Prof. Dr. Yulianeta, M.Pd.</a></li>
